message:
Share button works!

The share button works! (Ideas are correctly passed to apps)
Except with Facebook...for some reason

Apps that will take the string correctly (for sure):

-Gmail
-Email
-Drive (but names get truncated...but that's on Drive's end)
-Keep
-Google+
-Facebook Messenger
-Hangouts

message:

-Clicking on something in the stack puts it in the GUI
